snippet: John Pizzarelli and Jessica Molaskey’s new show, “This Must Be the Place?,” explores the concept of home with an awareness that its solidity is illusory.
abstract: Stephen Holden reviews performance of John Pizzarelli and Jessica Molaskey cabaret show This Must Be the Place? at Cafe Carlyle.
lead_paragraph: John Pizzarelli and Jessica Molaskey’s new show, “This Must Be the Place?,” explores the concept of home with an awareness that its solidity is illusory.

headline.seo: John Pizzarelli and Jessica Molaskey at Café Carlyle
headline.main: The Many Notions of Home, Redefined and Questioned in an Evening of Songs
